data.description: Great two-story home on corner lot in Rolling Oaks South IV! Welcome home to a foyer with arch doorways to the formal dining area and to the living room. Kitchen has NEW electric range, microwave, and dishwasher! Spacious living room with fireplace that flows into breakfast nook and kitchen. Vinyl flooring in dining room. Oversized utility room connected to mudroom great for storage. Upstairs game/rec room and bedrooms. Master suite has walk-in closet, separate walk-in shower, and whirlpool tub! NEW gutters with leaf guard and NEW HVAC with insulation! Beautiful backyard. This home is well-maintained and ready for you!!
